data.title: Martin Lawrence 1993
data.meta_description: The "You So Crazy" Tour from 1993. I swear, my Dad and I were the ONLY White people in the old Performing Arts Center @ the Aladdin. This was back when Martin had his TV show and the "edginess" that he earned from his "Def Comedy" appearances. I remember making the walk of shame back to the Bally's parking Lot after the concert, my lame whiteness having been immortalized in public.
